# Live mode needs to get past Home Depot's Akamai Bot Manager. A local browser
# is blocked (403 on product pages), so point this at a hosted "scraping browser"
# that handles Akamai (residential IPs + sensor solving). Our Playwright scraper
# connects to it over CDP - no other code changes needed.
#
# Examples (use the CDP / websocket endpoint from your provider):
#   Bright Data Scraping Browser: wss://brd-customer-<id>-zone-<zone>:<pass>@brd.superproxy.io:9222
#   ZenRows Scraping Browser:     wss://browser.zenrows.com?apikey=<key>
#
# Leave unset to use a local browser (works in dev, but HD will 403 live scrapes).
SCRAPING_BROWSER_CDP_URL=
